310
00:21:49,750 --> 00:21:51,583
I believe in only one thing.

311
00:21:53, 41 --> 00:21:55,  0
My late master's words.

312
00:21:56,458 --> 00:21:58,625
Master Ichigen said to be certain.

313
00:21:59,333 --> 00:22:02,  0
I have not yet given up making certain.

314
00:22:02, 41 --> 00:22:04,833
That is why I have no intention of allowing the final curtain to fall.

315
00:22:06,416 --> 00:22:09,333
What about you, Shiro?

316
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:13,916
Don't give up, huh?

317
00:22:15,416 --> 00:22:16,375
You're right.

318
00:22:17,125 --> 00:22:19,500
Your Master Ichigen speaks the truth.

319
00:22:20,916 --> 00:22:25,208
In that case, I will allow you to repeat his words.

320
00:22:26,708 --> 00:22:31,541
Saying Master Ichigen's blessed words will cleanse your soul.

321
00:22:35, 83 --> 00:22:35,875
Creepy.

322
00:24:09,875 --> 00:24:10,916
It's me, Neko!

323
00:24:10,958 --> 00:24:11,875
Guess what, guess what?

324
00:24:11,916 --> 00:24:16, 41
Lots of Blue people stormed in and then, things went flash!

